get.description:
This machine learning API is based on a prediction model that takes the input of the user -time, carrier, airport and aircraft information- and predict the segment where the flight is likely to lay.

## Request example:
<pre><code>
GET https://test.api.amadeus.com/v1/travel/predictions/flight-delay?originLocationCode=NCE&destinationLocationCode=IST&departureDate=2020-08-01&departureTime=18:20:00&arrivalDate=2020-08-01&arrivalTime=22:15:00&aircraftCode=321&carrierCode=TK&flightNumber=1816&duration=PT31H10M
</code></pre>

